### Product API Test (Refactored v2)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4001/api/v1
@adminToken = (ใส่ Token ของคุณที่นี่)

### 1. [Public] ค้นหาและกรองสินค้า (พร้อม Validation)
# ทดสอบ minPrice ติดลบ (ควร Error 400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?minPrice=-100
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. [Admin] สร้างสินค้าใหม่ (Notebook)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/products
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="brand"

MSI
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="modelName"

Katana GF66
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="price"

35000
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="category"

Notebook
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="stock"

10
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="sku"

MSI-KATANA-001
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

Gaming laptop with RTX 3050
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="specifications"

{"CPU": "Intel i7", "RAM": "16GB", "Storage": "512GB SSD"}
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="product.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./test-images/product-sample-1.png
--boundary--

### 3. [Admin] อัปเดตสินค้าแบบบางส่วน (PATCH)
# แก้ไข RAM และ ลบฟิลด์ Storage ทิ้ง
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/products/{{product_id_here}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "specifications": {
        "RAM": "32GB",
        "Storage": ""
    }
}
